- Define IAM role within account or cross account.
- Define which principals can access this IAM role
- Security Token Service: To retrieve cred and impersonate the IAM role you have to access using AssumeRoleAPI
 Temporary between 15min to 1 hr


Used when:
1) IAM user in one account access resource in another account both owned by you.
2) Access to IAM users in AWS accounts owned by 3rd parties
3) Provide access for services offered by AWS to AWS resources
4) Provide access for externally auth users (identity federation)
5) Revoke active session